This is a demo file for pandoc-crossref. With this filter, you can
cross-reference figures (see fig.
 \ref{figure1}, \ref{figure2}, \ref{figure3}), display equations (see
eq.  \ref{eqn1}) and tables (see tbl.  \ref{table1})

